### Welcome to the Infineon RGB Shield Library 
#by Inderpreet Singh

```
$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

If you're using the GitHub for Mac, simply sync your repository and you'll see the new branch.

### Authors and Contributors
First Author @inderpreet

### Support or Contact
This library is distributed under GPLv2 which means you use it at your own risk. If you want to contribute, fork it, modify it and send me a pull request.

I'm at inderpreet.github.io
